=head1 NAME

LOG_AND_CASU - creates a nightlog and casu export files

=head1 DESCRIPTION
                                                                                
Calls _COPY_COMPRESSED_ to create the casu export files and _NIGHT_LOG_ to 
create a nightlog in $ORAC_DATA_OUT.

Intended to be run after dawn, possibly with a seperate $ORAC_DATA_OUT to 
the overnight run. (PH)

=head1 AUTHOR
                                                                                
Paul Hirst <p.hirst@jach.hawaii.edu>

=cut

_WFCAM_HELLO_
_COPY_COMPRESSED_
_NIGHT_LOG_ LONG=1 OUT=1
